syntax = "proto3";
package rummy100;

/*
    MSGID定义说明,rummy和赛事rummy在PB上保持同步,
    客户端请求协议point、deal、match point、match deal都是15300-15399
    服务端区分返回协议：
        point           15300-15399
        deal            15500-15599
        match point     15600-15699
        match deal      15700-15799  
    服务端通过CheckPointToDealMsgID来区分返回协议
*/

